{"tid":2301931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"首宗国安法被告手足唐英傑有嘢想同大家講","createTime":"2020-11-26T16:43:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T11:27:32.000Z","uid":147376,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"21342cd4e016cfa25f9897624e9216821412df85","tid":2301931,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T16:43:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201124/4SXSZON3RVCO7OXFGP6Z3MDFF4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201124%2F4SXSZON3RVCO7OXFGP6Z3MDFF4%2F&d=ME9RTGLMBg%2Fi%2BHfTLk0cjJnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=e37521ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201124%2F4SXSZON3RVCO7OXFGP6Z3MDFF4%2F&h=66511449\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201124/4SXSZON3RVCO7OXFGP6Z3MDFF4/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首名被控違反「港區國安法」的抗爭者唐英傑，因在7.1駕駛插有「光復香港 時代革命」旗幟電單車，被控煽動他人分裂國家及恐怖活動，現正還押於荔枝角收押所。。即將離任的社福界議員邵家臻今日（24日）到訪收押所。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n邵引述與唐英傑的對話，指對方在獄中看了《坐監記》、《李登輝：我的餘生與民主之路》等著作，現正讀第二次世界大戰歷史；又指唐已經適應獄中生活，也對即將面對的判刑神態自若<br />\n<br />\n對於仍在抗爭的手足，唐英傑勉勵要「等候丶忍耐」；至於有意離港的人，邵家臻引述唐坦然說：「人心裏有香港，邊度都係香港」，呼籲要學習昔日的猶太人。"},{"pid":"4218e996e8b2a00a12a5087e08296782db5d9178","tid":2301931,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T16:44:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"938f23851b5226dbbef7c41b69acc2483e27a44c","tid":2301931,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T16:44:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1781f4bf3ea1dc780181126863a3dfe1fa46e4d8","tid":2301931,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T16:44:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=